      "writtenOn": "2017-05-15T18:40:15Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "1. The native header that I see just has 30, not a casted 30, and we should duplicate what the native header does (otherwise, things get really confusing based on whether you’re using the native header or our compat header).\n\n2. All comments from compat/android/sys/ptrace.h apply. We probably don’t need this file at all.",
      "revId": "86ccb582c47070c865ada7ba998609af66e43cae",
