      "writtenOn": "2017-05-15T18:40:15Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "At the ARM specification level, floating-point support is optional. I don’t know if Android goes beyond that to mandate it, but I can’t definitely say that this should be considered an error condition.",
      "revId": "86ccb582c47070c865ada7ba998609af66e43cae",
