      "message": "Kernel limitation, maybe just stay quiet about it. You can keep the message if you’d like, but it shouldn’t be an ERROR and should be a little more descriptive than this, because seeing “Not implemented” in our log message makes it seem like it’s something that we can implement but haven’t, but this one isnt’ on us at all.",
